headline: Coinbase Global Stock (COIN) Prepares for S&P 500 Listing With 16% Spike
summary: Cryptoeconomy enabler Coinbase Global (COIN) rallied 16% over the past five days to celebrate its public listing on the S&P 500 index, scheduled for next week. Coinbase’s addition to the S&P 500 marks a historic milestone as the first cryptocurrency exchange included in the index, symbolizing a step toward mainstream acceptance of crypto.
